Obito throws the opponent up in the air while using his Wood Release: Cutting Technique. The opponent lands and Obito wraps them in a wooden ball. Madara then summons his Tengai Shinsei, while Obito uses [[Kamui]] to escape from the blast, which crashes down on the opponent.
